      "side": 1,
      "message": "Follow the structure of the projects around you: check out into crashpad/third_party/lss/lss. In third_party/lss, provide a README.crashpad file. You can follow the example of zlib, gtest, and mini_chromium.\n\nThe “outer” LSS directory is the place to receive the LSS checkout in DEPS, and also a place to put Crashpad-specific files like README.crashpad and any local .gyp files, forwarding headers, etc.\n\nYou will also note that this entire section is sorted, so don’t put LSS at the end, put it before mini_chromium.",
      "revId": "2ae855380b2b4a0eefbd86ad8bb83b47ee6299d9",
