      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is quirky, it does a pass to interpret the number, and then calls StringToNumber() which does…another pass to interpret the number.\n\n(Maybe this was better with stdio operations?)",
      "revId": "2ae855380b2b4a0eefbd86ad8bb83b47ee6299d9",
