      "message": "At first, I was going to suggest using base::FreeDeleter in base/memory/free_deleter.h instead of having a local addition, but I see that you’re concerned with a char** here, not a char*. OK, got it.",
      "revId": "2ae855380b2b4a0eefbd86ad8bb83b47ee6299d9",
