      "side": 1,
      "message": "ptrace Init? That gave me pause for a few moments. It seemed like an oddly-written function name.\n\nSay “cannot ptrace /init” (path makes it clear what init you’re talking about) or “ptrace pid 1” (pid makes it clear too, especially in light of the comment that follows).",
      "revId": "2ae855380b2b4a0eefbd86ad8bb83b47ee6299d9",
