      "message": "1. You don’t need to exclude all of net, only http_transport_test.cc. All of the rest of the net tests pass on Android and other Linuxes.\n2. You only need to exclude http_transport_test.cc on Android, not on other Linuxes, since https://chromium.googlesource.com/crashpad/crashpad/+/777e36014f766f245f9ea3f37b6d02e4054588ef.",
