        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-03-08T16:47:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Be precise with regular expressions. Don’t begin with (^|/) because we know exactly what this path is going to look like: it starts with “numeric” (as written in sources above), so just go with ^. Backslash-escape the dot and anchor the end with a $. These comments apply to the Android-only exclude of http_transport_test.cc as well.",
